content.description: This fun slab and warm up boulder is right off the trail as you walk towards The West Boulder. It has a tall, eastern-facing slab with lots of options. The north side has a wide crack, a few arete problems, and a blocky corner the south side with one or 2 lines on it. You can also do a traverse from the south to the north side going across the slab. The East Boulder can be seen from the top of the boulder.
